Saat lagu itu berakhir, sayangku

15
00:01:15,397 --> 00:01:16,257
{\fad(300,0)\fnArabic Typesetting\fs30\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFF00FF&\blur7}♪ ستضحك ♪

16
